      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.zITucvIlaUKx6hta]{Accord}</p>\n<p>As a reaction when an effect simultaneously affects at least two linked allies (or you and at least one linked ally) and provides a saving throw to reduce its effects, you can spend 1 Resolve Point from your communal pool to bolster the linked creatures’ saving throws. Determine which of the affected linked allies has the highest saving throw modifier against the effect’s first save; each linked ally affected by the effect uses that saving throw modifier instead of their own modifier.</p>"
